{"tid":2417723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警告各國於南海航行   解放軍又在黃海渤海軍演　宣佈21日至28日禁航警告","createTime":"2021-02-22T06:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T06:10:38.000Z","uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"722d6f55ff42a78f723ca4b85c640579e2ad0b5a","tid":2417723,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"中國大連海事局今天（21日）發佈航行警告指稱，從今天（21日）下午4時至28日下午4時，渤海海峽、黃海北部的部份海域將有軍事任務，禁止駛入。座標為「38&deg;51&prime;41&Prime;N 121&deg;38&prime;12&Prime;E」、「38&deg;34&prime;12&Prime;N 121&deg;38&prime;12&Prime;E」、「38&deg;33&prime;55&Prime;N 121&deg;07&prime;51&Prime;E」、「38&deg;48&prime;13&Prime;N 121&deg;14&prime;03&Prime;E」，並警告船隻禁止駛入相關範圍內政部長。<br />\n<br />\n本月稍早，大連海事局也公告將從2月7日16時至2月21日16時在渤海、黃海舉行軍事演習。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡《聯合早報》報導指，今天開年以來，解放軍密集在渤海、黃海、東海三大海域演習，一般認為，解放軍高調宣告演習，是因應近期美國海軍航艦也頻繁進出台灣海峽、南海海域航行，較勁意味濃厚。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"7ab30b54a46cf91bfd8c4ca812bb44f2545df18d","tid":2417723,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210221/MZPIBUVZCVEW3PXTOED4Q77OLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210221%2FMZPIBUVZCVEW3PXTOED4Q77OLM%2F&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=6fc08242\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210221%2FMZPIBUVZCVEW3PXTOED4Q77OLM%2F&h=62edcabd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210221/MZPIBUVZCVEW3PXTOED4Q77OLM/</a>"}]}